text: Tengan Paciencia (also named Tengan Paciencia: The Mixtape) [English: Have Patience] is the fifth compilation album by Puerto Rican reggaeton duo Jowell & Randy, released digitally in January 2010 as a prelude to their next studio album, El Momento, which was released in April 2010. The album contains 19 songs. == Track list == #"Intro" #"Tapú Tapú" (Ft. De La Ghetto) #"Caca E Vaca" #"Se Enciende El Party" (Ft. Guelo Star) #"ChocoPop" (Ft.
